    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this thing since day one, always kept it garaged and kept the interior sparkling clean. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
