    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating and a clear bra protecting the front end from any road debris. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show absolutely zero bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent is still present. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous adherence to the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule, with all records organized in a comprehensive binder. There are no scratches on the alloy wheels, no chips in the glass, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or grime. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been treated with the utmost care and respect.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in superlative condition, this vehicle exemplifies the highest standards of automotive excellence. Every facet, from its pristine exterior finish to its flawlessly maintained mechanical systems, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade specimen that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state. For the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity, this offering stands as the definitive choice.",
