      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in pristine, showroom-level condition and has been babied since day one. Seriously, it looks and drives like it\u2019s brand new\u2014not a scratch or smudge in sight! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
