    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) in documented mint condition. This specimen retains the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting optimal compression and linear power delivery across the rev range. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally flawless, featuring its original lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension and 50/50 weight distribution. Recent professional servicing includes a comprehensive vacuum system refresh and cooling system optimization to mitigate heat soak. An unmolested, investment-grade example for the serious enthusiast.",
